oai_dc:dc.dc:title: ENDANGERED SPECIES LIST
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: n/a, n/a
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The following list of eandangered species of birds is complete as of October 27, 1976 .Only thoe birds listed are recognized by the U.S. Government as endangered and consequentlysubject to regulation in interstate and foreign commerce.The list is published for the information of AFA members and may be used as a handyreference guide. It should be noted that species may be added to or deleted from the listin the future. Notice of such action will be published in the Watchbird.
